||A^k|| \leq ||A||^k
B = \sum_{k=0}^\infty \frac{(At)^k}{k!}
\sum_{k=0}^\infty \bigg|\bigg| \frac{(At)^k}{k!}\bigg|\bigg|\leq \sum_{k=0}^\infty \frac{(||A||t)^k}{k!} = e^{||A||t}
